            <title>[SPARK-24621] WebUI - application &apos;name&apos; urls point to http instead of https (even when ssl enabled)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-24621</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See attached&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ApplicationID correctly points to DNS url&lt;br/&gt;
but Name points to IP address&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Update: I found setting SPARK_PUBLIC_DNS to DNS hostname will make Name point to DNS. BUT it will use http instead of https!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
